# ☁️ Cloud Computing

## Cloud vs On-Premise

### On-Premise
- Physical servers managed by company
- High hardware and maintenance cost
- Manual scaling
- Limited flexibility

### Cloud Computing
- Infrastructure over internet
- Pay-as-you-go pricing
- Easy scalability
- High availability
- Faster deployment

