# 🌐 AWS Networking & VPC

## VPC Components
- VPC
- Public Subnet
- Private Subnet
- Route Tables
- Internet Gateway
- NAT Gateway
- Security Groups
- NACL

## Important Concepts

### Route Table
Controls traffic routing inside VPC.

### Internet Gateway (IGW)
Provides internet connectivity to public subnets.

### NAT Gateway
Allows private EC2 instances to access internet securely.

### Security Group
Stateful firewall at EC2 level.

### NACL
Stateless firewall at subnet level.

---

# 🔥 Stateful vs Stateless

## Stateful
- Remembers connection state
- Example: Security Group

## Stateless
- Does not remember previous requests
- Example: NACL

